description: This 2000 Ford Mustang has 43,395 miles and has been with the current owner for the past 13 years!  It's a 2 owner,  adult driven car,  with a very interesting twist on the power plant.  The original owner of the car had a Procharger centrifugal supercharger system  professionally installed on the car.  It's a P-1SC model supercharger which is a self contained oiling system developed by Procharger so there is no tapping into the oil pan for a return line or hooking up an oil supply line.  It's also a very efficient and productive unit with hp gains in the 50%-80% range over stock.  The estimated horsepower on this car would be in the 300 range give or take, not to bad for a 6 cylinder!  It really is a blast to drive as the RPMS rise the car really goes!  If you're looking for a very nice reliable driver that has never been raced this car would fall into that category.  The performance red paint is in nice shape, especially for being 17 years old with only a couple small dings by the drivers front fender that one really needs to look for to see.  The interior has had seat covers on it the majority of its life so the original fabric buckets seats are in great shape as well as the carpeting and rest of interior.  Cobra wheels, some emblems, and a wing have been added to give it a high performance look.  The underside of the car is clean and floor pans are solid.  We do have a Carfax confirming mileage, no accidents and 2 owners so buy with confidence.  Feel free to call us at 507-386-1726 or email '

description: In 2005 Ford redesigned the Mustang and Saleen was right behind them with their own design which turned out one of the sleekest ponys to this day. Here is a 2006 Saleen S281 Convertible that has just become available for sale! This is a beautiful triple black convertible powered by a supercharged 4.6ltr. 3v SOHC engine that is rated at 400 hp and 425 lb-ft of torque. If you've ever seen or heard one of these cars you know how special they really are. If you've ever had the chance to spend some time behind the wheel in one you'll know why Saleen has the saying ''Power in the Hands of a Few'' If you would like to be ''one of those few'' here is your chance! This car comes with the upgraded chrome wheels as well as cross drilled and slotted rotors added up front. The rear bumper sports the SALEEN logo and has the great looking center exhaust. This particular Saleen has had a pioneer stereo system professionally installed with subs added in the trunk. Please see the trunk pictures listed, this installation was done cleanly and the trunk is still very usable and looks great with a custom mirrored Saleen custom deck lid insert. This particular Convertible is 1 of 416 Saleen convertible made in 2006. It is absolutely stunning in triple black with the Saleen graphics, ground effects and interior setting this car of and pronouncing It's not just any Mustang! Want to know more?
